text: Pavel Menšík (born 15 March 1968) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Olomouc
